These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-1::.
Sport: swimming, golf, lacrosse
1. Sport:golf is on the right of Sport:lacrosse##1
2. Sport:swimming is on the far right##1
3. Sport:swimming is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |   3   |
| Sport   | lacrosse | golf | swimming |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-2::.
Food: pear, pumpkin, cherry
1. Food:pumpkin is in an odd position##4
2. Food:pear is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Food   | pear | cherry | pumpkin |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-3::.
Hobby: collecting, video-games, gardening
1. Hobby:video-games is in an even position##4
2. Hobby:video-games is on the left or right of Hobby:gardening##3
3. Hobby:gardening is on the right of Hobby:video-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3       |
| Hobby   | collecting | video-games | gardening |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-4::.
